video.title: Jenni Rivera: Mariposa de Barrio
video.synopsis: This drama follows Mexican-American singer Jenni Rivera's unlikely rise from suicidal pregnant teen and abused wife to banda superstar.

episodes.synopsis: On September 3, 2011, Jenni Rivera started to taste real career success when she gave a sold-out show in Los Angeles. She had always dreamed of it.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Jenni’s brothers find her dying. Trino is at the eye of the storm and his life is miserable. Pedro takes the next step in getting custody of Chiquis.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Pedro visits Jenni with the whole family and they tell her that Trino left because of Chiquis. Jenni calls home and hears horrible news.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Doña Rosa finds a note that will result in serious consequences. Jenni has her first public performance. Meanwhile Trino tries to get closer to her.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Jenni goes into therapy and re-examines her life and the hell she went through with Trino. Trino moves heaven and earth to talk to Jenni.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Pedro sees a brilliant future for Jenni and offers her a job at his record label, but her mother won’t allow it. Trino gives his ex a present.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Jenni decides who she’ll celebrate her graduation with. Trino, still obsessed with her, gets drunk and causes problems.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: When visiting Trino, Jenni confronts an enemy and surprises Don Pedro and Doña Rosa with some unexpected news. Tere and Trino fight.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Convinced she owes Chiquis a family, Jenni gets back with Trino, who tries his best to change and show her love. However, his dark side resurfaces.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Trino’s unhealthy jealousy makes Jenni’s life a living hell. Meanwhile, Rosa is worried about her. Ramona thinks Pete is cheating on her.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Jenni gives in and falls into Trino’s trap. Feeling regretful, she takes a pregnancy test. Ramona makes a drastic decision.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Jenni goes to see Trino and tells him that she’s pregnant with his child, but he refuses to recognize the baby as his. Pete is destroyed in a fight.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Trino abuses Jenni until her graduation day and in the middle of the ceremony, she gets contractions. A study reveals the sex of the baby.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Trino steals Rosie’s innocence, who is looking to leave her home. Later, he hits Jenni. Pete decides to devote his life to God.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: After breaking things off with Trino, Jenni goes to get her belongings and then looks for a different job. Meanwhile, he proposes to María.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Trino finds out that Jenni is about to give birth and wants to make up. Jenni and Chiquis move in with her parents and she surprises Trino with María.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Trino refuses to recognize Jackie as his daughter. Ramona faints and the paramedics take her to the hospital. Jenni finds a new way to make money.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: Jenni becomes a successful real estate agent and buys a house. Meanwhile, Trino loses his job but wants Jenni back. Pedro cheats on Rosa.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Jenni’s success in real estate helps Trino find a new job opportunity. The couple moves into a new house. Rosie confesses that Trino did “bad things”.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Pedro tells Trino that the baby was born and he celebrates the arrival of Trinidad but complains that Jenni is fat. Rosa tells Jenni to leave him.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: After another attack by Trino, Jenni has him arrested. Chalino gets into trouble and Marisela is upset.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Jenni makes a new record as a gift for her father’s birthday, while she distances herself from Trino. Rosa and Pedro disagree about Jenni’s future.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Lupillo gets into the music business. Jenni starts singing. While Chiquis is bathing, Trino enters the bathroom. Rosa suspects he has a secret.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: The Ensenada Mardi Gras is the ideal time for Jenni to launch her career. In spite of a standing ovation, the organizer doesn’t pay her.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: Jenni has her first disappointment as a singer, and composes a corrido called "La Chacalosa." She asks Trino for a loan but he imposes a condition.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: Jenni is so upset by her family situation that she considers quitting singing. After Marisela insists, Jenni accepts her invitation.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Jenni sings La Chacalosa and everyone applauds. She feels attracted to an admirer that treats her like a diva. Pedro visits his son in jail.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: Jenni decides to go out with her admirer, Juan López. Rosa worries about Jenni’s new friend. Trino runs into his rival.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: Radio-owner Pepe Garza is interested in Lupillo but not in Jenni. She makes it clear that she is a singer in her own right. Trino takes the children.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Juan López moves in with Jenni and asks her for a loan to pay his debts and support his children. When Trino finds out, he swears revenge.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Juan López and Jenni start having problems. Juan shows his true colors and she is furious. She hits him with a brick and the police get involved.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: A popular announcer makes Jenni an offer. Juan López gets into serious trouble. Trino hopes he can work things out with his ex.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Jenni looks for a radio opportunity so she goes to two interviews. Pedro makes a video to promote her. Juan’s parents take Jenni’s side.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: Jenni is kidnapped and raped and gets depressed. López gets out of prison, but his relationship with Jenni has changed. She keeps the rape a secret.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Juan López is ordered to be deported, but there is one way out: marrying Jenni. Trino starts legal action to keep his children.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: A charismatic seer announces that Rosie was sexually abused as a child and is suffering, in front of the whole Rivera family. She confesses to Jenni.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Rosie tells Jenni that Trino abused her and Chiquis. She wants justice and takes a knife. The Riveras want revenge.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: Jenni reports the sexual abuse suffered by the girls and asks the authorities to detain Trino, but it’s not possible.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: Jenni loses focus on her marriage due to problems with Trino. Feeling ignored, Juan López becomes seductive at work.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Gus knows that Juan is cheating on Jenni. When she finds out, she hires a private investigator. Jenni wants to get revenge on her ex.
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Jenni sees Juan throw away the food she made him and go out to lunch with two women. It is over between them. Jenni gets a record contract with Sony.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Fonovisa makes Jenni an offer but after her long struggle to make it in the music industry, something unexpected could end her career.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: A pregnant Jenni leaves her job in real estate and goes on tour in the U.S.A. Her song Dear Partner becomes a hit. The media publishes false news.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: The superstar triumphs in Los Angeles and will celebrate the 15th anniversary of Don Francisco’s show. Problems with Juan keep Jenni away.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Jenni climbs higher in the music industry, receiving a Latin Grammy nomination. She talks about being raped on Don Francisco’s show.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Jenni accuses Juan of cheating again, but he denies it. Rosa dreams that Pedro and Jessica are together and hires Jenni’s private detective.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Rosa tells the boys that Pedro is cheating on her and kicks him out of the house. Juan and Jenni are on the brink of divorce.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: Close to divorce, Jenni meets a radio producer who impresses her. He has managed several famous artists.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: Jenni’s first concert is sold out and wildly successful. The public is enthralled. Juan fights for half of their assets.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: After Rosie is let down by Ricky she starts to drink and attempts suicide. Jenni wants to record an album in English, but Don Pedro doesn’t agree.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: Fernie, Jenni’s new boyfriend, rents an apartment for them. Jenni’s divorce is over but the press stalks her because of Juan’s alimony suit.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: Jenni introduces Fernie to her family. Rosa doesn’t think he is a good choice for her but Jenni tells her that he sells movies and makes big money.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Jenni wants to launch a cosmetic line. She suspects Fernie is cheating and kicks him out. He asks his mother Consuelo for advice.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: Although he is unfaithful, Pedro Rivera cares about his family. Rosa faints and a kiss on her forehead seals his commitment to stay with her forever.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: Although Fernie and Jenni were distanced by the fans that tormented Consuelo, they move into his apartment. Andres and Rosie become a couple.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: At Jenni’s new record launch for Simply the Best, Andrés has an attack of jealousy. Jenni wants to create a foundation.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: Jenni enjoys her success with a gold and platinum record, but she gets into trouble after mentioning a possible duet. A mysterious call upsets Rosa.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: After Jenni’s statements, the press seeks a scandal and announces an unprecedented fight. Andrés threatens to reveal Rosie’s secret.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Jenni is interviewed on TV and gets revenge by singing La mentada cantada. In Miami, Fernie is gone and she kicks him out for cheating.
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Jenni gives a concert at a sold-out Kodak Theatre. She presents her cosmetic line, Divina, whose funds will go to the Jenni Rivera Love Foundation.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Rosie is missing. Juan and Brenda don’t want to involve the police but they find her clothes. Later, they tell the family which unites to find her.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: Rosie and Brenda see Trino with a woman, but he flees. Now the Riveras publicly report him. Fernie fights with Jenni and leaves the house.
episodes.title: Todos van por Trino

episodes.synopsis: The Riveras’ interview with Charytín, where they report Trino’s rapes, causes accusations against Jenni. Lupillo offers 50,000 dollars for clues.
episodes.title: Denuncian al violador

episodes.synopsis: Trino feels trapped. Celina tells him to turn himself in but others tell him to leave the country. One of Jenni’s fans gives him away.
episodes.title: Acorralan a Trino

episodes.synopsis: Fernando says good-bye to Jenni’s children and tells them the separation is final. They seek a lawyer for Trino, while he abuses Maria.
episodes.title: Ruptura

episodes.synopsis: The FBI corners Trino. He’ll have to face the evidence against him and needs a lawyer. Jenni suffers after she is almost kidnapped.
episodes.title: El FBI detrás de Trino

episodes.synopsis: The trial starts and Trino declares himself not guilty. The judge sets bail at a million dollars. His family starts seeing Jenni as a manipulator.
episodes.title: Trino insiste en su inocencia

episodes.synopsis: Chiquis isn’t sure if she wants to be part of Trino’s trial, but she’s convinced she should. The Riveras worry that Trino will be released on bail.
episodes.title: Rosie, testigo clave

episodes.synopsis: Trino’s family says that Jenni is crazy and that Rosie and Chiquis are lying. Rosie feels ashamed, but everyone is proud of what she did.
episodes.title: La defensa de Trino

episodes.synopsis: The Riveras come together on the day of the hearing. Trino flaunts his innocence, trying to show that they have slandered him.
episodes.title: Trino en el estrado

episodes.synopsis: Jenni and Fernie get back together. She asks him to join her at a club where El recodo is playing, but they fight again and she almost kills him.
episodes.title: Fernie es otro

episodes.synopsis: Fernie stays the night with Jenni and tells her that he uses crystal meth, but can quit if he wants to. Trino’s lawyers have an ace up their sleeve.
episodes.title: Otra decepción para Jenni

episodes.synopsis: Fernie goes to rehabilitation but when he gets out, he suffers from paranoia and has an accident. Jenni cancels her show to go to see him.
episodes.title: Alucinaciones

episodes.synopsis: If Pedro doesn’t give Rosa her part of the company in the divorce, her daughter threatens to quit. Jenni is nominated for a Billboard award.
episodes.title: La disquera en disputa

episodes.synopsis: The jury rapidly returns with their verdict, but Trino stays in prison until sentencing. Jenni wins the Billboard award.
episodes.title: Alegato final

episodes.synopsis: Clara is a prostitute to pay for her sick son. The foundation changes their lives: it will pay for the boy’s surgeries and her university degree.
episodes.title: La generosidad de Jenni

episodes.synopsis: Jacquie leaves home even though everyone tells her not to. Jenni wakes up in a hospital after contracting appendicitis. The DEA arrests Juan.
episodes.title: Más sufrimiento para Jenni

episodes.synopsis: Personal problems affect Jenni's musical career. Fernie goes to Las Vegas and Juan is put in jail. Esteban Loaiza tries to adapt to his new life.
episodes.title: Flaquea la carrera de Jenni

episodes.synopsis: Jenni makes a drastic decision about her new album, which draws her father's fury. Pete and Gustavo consider Jenni's possible retirement.
episodes.title: La ira de Pedro

episodes.synopsis: Jacquie and Danny try to cross the border illegally. The erotic video could appear on the internet any day and Jenni preps her family.
episodes.title: Juegan a ser coyotes

episodes.synopsis: Jenni has to pay a $50,000 bail if she wants to go free after fighting with a fan. Later, Jenni meets Esteban Loaiza during the concert.
episodes.title: Microfonazo en defensa propia

episodes.synopsis: Jenni moves house. Everyone except Mikey wants to stop Esteban from seducing her. The diva is a finalist in the Latin Billboard awards.
episodes.title: La conquista

episodes.synopsis: Jenni tells the press about her relationship with Esteban. She considers singing a duet with Juan but Pedro thinks it could be a conflict of interest.
episodes.title: Amor a todas luces

episodes.synopsis: Loaiza admits that he lied. Jenni travels to Mexico to perform and has problems with the law. Graciela Beltrán tries to destroy Jenni publicly.
episodes.title: Jenni rompe con Esteban

episodes.synopsis: Esteban wants to make up with Jenni but she rejects him. Chiquis takes Jacquie to the doctor, who confirms her suspicions. Juan isn't doing well.
episodes.title: Jenni, inflexible

episodes.synopsis: Jenni's representatives are doubtful about her new musical endeavor. Jenni wants to meet her grandchild's father but Jacquie doesn't know who it is.
episodes.title: Proyecto: “La Gran Señora”

episodes.synopsis: Jacquie's baby Jaylah is born and someone claims paternity. Jenni's album debut is a huge success. There are wedding rumors about Jenni and Esteban.
episodes.title: Crece la familia Rivera

episodes.synopsis: Esteban invites Jenni to have dinner at a restaurant where he is planning to propose. Jenni is nominated for the Billboard and Lo Nuestro awards.
episodes.title: Una sorpresa para Jenni

episodes.synopsis: Jenni is alarmed while she's getting ready for her next concert. Mikey gets into trouble with a minor and the girl's mother complains to Jenni.
episodes.title: Amenaza de secuestro

episodes.synopsis: The alleged romance between Chiquis and Loaiza comes to light and opinions are divided. Jenni triumphs at Arena Monterrey.
episodes.title: Enredos de familia

episodes.synopsis: Chiquis is depressed by Jenni's accusation. The diva dedicates the song Paloma negra to her daughter and predicts her own future in Monterrey.
episodes.title: Ovación y despedida
